-- ANZ Bank May Decide on Korea Exchange Bank Stake Next Month, Chosun Says
-- B y   E u n k y u n g   S e o
-- 2010-09-28T22:16:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-28/anz-bank-may-decide-on-korea-exchange-bank-stake-next-month-chosun-says.html
Australia & New Zealand Banking
Group Ltd. may decide on the purchase of a stake in Korea
Exchange Bank next month, the Chosun Ilbo reported, without
saying where it got the information. ANZ has showed strong
interest after completing its due diligence review on the South
Korean bank as it seeks to purchase a shareholding held by U.S.-
based Lone Star Funds, the Korean-language newspaper reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Eunkyung Seo in Seoul at 
 eseo3@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
